                    <desc>
                      Scribal intervention:
                       words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#12r #20r #43r #44v" facs="014 022 045 047"/>, etc.);
                       lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#10r #12v #23r #50r" facs="012 015 025 052"/>, etc.);
